Dear U2.Com Member,

Tickets for the final two Elevation 2001 USA shows go on sale today,
Saturday - and there are still tickets available for the other six shows
added to the tour last week.

Tickets for the shows in Tampa (December 1st) and Miami (December 2nd)
which go on sale today and the shows in Sacramento (November 20th),
Phoenix (November 23rd), Dallas (November 25th), Kansas (November 27th),
St Louis (November28th) and Atlanta (November 30th) can all be bought
online at http://cc.com/


* Meanwhile Walk On, the third single to be released from All That You
Can't Leave Behind, is released worldwide outside the US from this Monday.
The track comes in several formats and already, a stunning acoustic version,
is garnering a lot or airplay.
Check our story here http://www.u2.com/lite/index_walkon.html


* What's Going On, the charity recording to benefit the fight against AIDS in
Africa and those affected by the September 11th events in the US, is also now
released in many territories. There are nine different mixes including Brian
Eno's stunning 'London' mix featuring Edge, Bono and Coldplay's Chris Martin.
Check our story here http://www.u2.com/lite/index_fight_aids.html


* Elevation, Live From Boston, the full length concert DVD, is also set to
hit stores within days. We've got the low-down on this amazing 2-DVD release -
as well as the full track-listing..
Click here for more. http://www.u2.com/lite/index_boston_dvd.html

* And don't forget to vote for U2 in the MY VH-I Music Awards.
Vote here - http://www.vh1.com/mymusic/2001/

...and in the Top Tour and the Top Rock categories in the BBC Top of the Pops
awards. Vote here - http://www.bbc.co.uk/totp/features/totp_awards/index.shtml


* For those of you looking for the complete set, there's a very cool new
charcoal 'elevation' t-shirt just arrived in the U2 Shop ( http://shop.u2.com/ )
while Zootopia, our community area, ?is hot with U2 chat from other acts
covering U2 songs to ticket swaps for the rest of the tour.
(Zootopia - http://zootopia.u2.com/ )



Best wishes


